Feature: Question page. On the question page the user is presented with a question that is relevant to the chosen level and game. There are options to Skip a question, get the next question and finish the game. Scores are displayed on the top right hand corner. The answer input area senses the answer to change the background colour (red or green)  indicating if the answer is right or wrong. The user can correct the answer to get a green background or skip/get the next question.

Background:
Given A user visits the maths game home page

